    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver despite showing its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a few small dings, and the interior shows moderate wear on the upholstery. Mechanically, the car starts and runs consistently, though it may soon require routine maintenance for suspension components and a minor oil seep. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle at a lower price point who doesn't mind some aesthetic imperfections.",
