    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting with my absolute favorite ride. It\u2019s been so reliable and still looks fantastic on the road! It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014well-maintained and ready for many more adventures. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love driving it as much as I have. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 32500.0,
